          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/b136dfacdbfad3318ad97408c84f8810_4680341152912171373.png",
                "key": "迅破槍勢",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "迅破槍勢"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">烈燒佑命護盾</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">烈燒佑命護盾</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">護盾</span></p><p>為我方出戰角色提供1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">護盾</span>。（可疊加，最多疊加到3點）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/375c5e00af78c34af064565c8c932329_3562400404218199484.png",
                "key": "烈燒佑命之侍護",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "烈燒佑命之侍護"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">烈燒佑命護盾</span>和<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">熾火大鎧</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">烈燒佑命護盾</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">護盾</span></p><p>為我方出戰角色提供1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">護盾</span>。（可疊加，最多疊加到3點）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">熾火大鎧</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方角色普通攻擊後：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">烈燒佑命護盾</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/47b82b01f63f39b206ba0c985d5de119_5449569441912519991.png",
                "key": "真紅熾火之大鎧",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "真紅熾火之大鎧"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_6990079912862801456.png",
                "key": "火元素傷害‧其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素傷害‧其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_6849550900414319226.png",
                "key": "火元素傷害‧其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_8857899907878614086.png",
                "title": "火元素傷害‧其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">護盾</span></p><p>此護盾所保護的角色受到傷害時，將會消耗護盾來抵消傷害。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_2976878280443094295.png",
